00:10:30.588 --> 00:10:32.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, yo... Por favor.</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:10:34.091 --> 00:10:34.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está bien.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:10:36.302 --> 00:10:37.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:10:38.304 --> 00:10:41.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sé que no soy tu padre biológico</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero quiero que sepas...</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:10:44.602 --> 00:10:45.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esto no es fácil.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:10:46.228 --> 00:10:49.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así que he escrito lo más importante.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:10:51.025 --> 00:10:51.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Una carta?</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:10:55.071 --> 00:10:56.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo entenderás en su momento.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:10:57.573 --> 00:10:59.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero que rompas el sello cuando...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:11:00.576 --> 00:11:02.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno, sabrás cuándo.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:11:04.205 --> 00:11:05.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando te hayan matado.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:11:06.540 --> 00:11:08.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La guerra viene con incertidumbre.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:11:08.668 --> 00:11:10.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué no haces algo al respecto?</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:11:11.087 --> 00:11:13.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No pueden hacer las paces?</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:11:13.547 --> 00:11:16.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- No es tan simple.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Lo veo bastante simple.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:11:17.426 --> 00:11:18.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No quieres morir.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:11:18.552 --> 00:11:21.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elfos y dragones no quieren morir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Están de acuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:11:22.598 --> 00:11:24.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay siglos de historia.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:11:25.393 --> 00:11:28.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Generaciones de errores y crímenes.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:11:28.521 --> 00:11:30.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En ambos lados.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:11:31.107 --> 00:11:33.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy responsable por algunos.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:11:33.818 --> 00:11:35.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He hecho cosas terribles.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:11:36.487 --> 00:11:38.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pensé que eran necesarias.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora no lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:11:41.701 --> 00:11:45.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero sé que pagaré el precio</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por mis decisiones.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:11:45.579 --> 00:11:49.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Debe haber un modo de arreglarlo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Es tarde.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:11:49.667 --> 00:11:52.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo hecho no puede ser deshecho.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:11:52.461 --> 00:11:54.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero eres rey.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Puedes hacer lo que sea.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:11:57.591 --> 00:12:01.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>La ilusión de la niñez es</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que los adultos tienen poder y libertad.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:12:01.846 --> 00:12:04.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero la verdad es lo opuesto.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:12:05.766 --> 00:12:07.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un niño es</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:12:07.852 --> 00:12:09.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>más libre que un rey.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:12:10.771 --> 00:12:12.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo regresaré el fin de semana, ¿sí?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:12:13.023 --> 00:12:14.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No tendré que abrirlo.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:12:15.776 --> 00:12:17.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuida a tu hermano.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:13:17.004 --> 00:13:18.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te equivocas sobre mí.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:13:21.008 --> 00:13:22.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedo hacerlo.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:13:24.261 --> 00:13:25.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo haré.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:13:42.947 --> 00:13:44.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ez? ¿Eres tú?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:13:46.075 --> 00:13:47.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Hola?</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:14:13.936 --> 00:14:16.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sabes que no te puedes escabullir.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:14:19.400 --> 00:14:22.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No eres quien pensé.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Eres de las que tienen largas...</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:14:22.945 --> 00:14:24.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No te gustan mis orejas?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:14:25.114 --> 00:14:28.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. Sí me gustan, supongo.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:14:28.784 --> 00:14:30.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hablaba de largas...</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:14:31.161 --> 00:14:33.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Espadas.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Hasta ahí.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:14:33.914 --> 00:14:35.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Busco a alguien.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:14:35.749 --> 00:14:38.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, ¿revisaste por allá?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:14:57.187 --> 00:14:58.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está detrás de mí.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:15:10.951 --> 00:15:13.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Oye, fuiste por la pierna!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:15:13.454 --> 00:15:14.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nada.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:15:19.376 --> 00:15:21.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Lord Viren! ¡Claudia! ¡Alguien!</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:30.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No tienes que morir.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:15:34.767 --> 00:15:38.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Solo hay dos blancos hoy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Dos? ¿De qué hablas?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:15:39.355 --> 00:15:40.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vine por el rey.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:44.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y también por su hijo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>el príncipe Ezran.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:15:44.652 --> 00:15:46.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedes. No es justo.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:15:46.362 --> 00:15:48.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué lastimarías</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a quien no hizo nada?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:15:49.031 --> 00:15:52.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los humanos mataron al Rey de los Dragones</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y rompieron su huevo,</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:15:52.993 --> 00:15:54.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>el Príncipe Dragón.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:15:54.870 --> 00:15:56.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se hará justicia.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:15:57.498 --> 00:15:58.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya veo.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:15:59.041 --> 00:16:01.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno, en ese caso me encontraste.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:16:02.628 --> 00:16:04.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy el príncipe Ezran.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:16:18.978 --> 00:16:21.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es buen día para ir de picnic.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:16:21.855 --> 00:16:23.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estamos de acuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:16:25.818 --> 00:16:29.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los elfos de luna son peligrosos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>luchadores de élite.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:16:29.238 --> 00:16:32.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajo luna llena,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>se vuelven casi invisibles.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:16:32.199 --> 00:16:34.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Penetran cualquier defensa.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:16:34.159 --> 00:16:37.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nada en los cinco reinos puede detenerlos.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:16:37.496 --> 00:16:38.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:16:38.831 --> 00:16:41.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te encontrarán y te matarán.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:16:42.334 --> 00:16:47.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- No ayudas, Viren.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Pero no tienes que ser tú.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:16:49.633 --> 00:16:54.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En las arenas del Desierto de Medianoche</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hay una misteriosa serpiente</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:16:54.680 --> 00:16:56.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>llamada la serpiente roba almas.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:16:57.141 --> 00:16:59.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tiene una dieta poco común.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:17:00.185 --> 00:17:03.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Muerde y consume el espíritu de su presa!</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:17:04.857 --> 00:17:06.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En nuestro último viaje a Xadia,</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:17:07.317 --> 00:17:10.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>obtuve un espécimen único.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:17:18.037 --> 00:17:20.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dos cabezas, dos mordidas,</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:17:20.497 --> 00:17:23.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>dos almas guardadas al mismo tiempo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y, a través de magia,</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:17:24.251 --> 00:17:27.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>puedo cambiar tu espíritu con otro.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:17:28.047 --> 00:17:31.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los elfos de luna encontrarán el cuerpo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del rey.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:17:31.925 --> 00:17:34.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero tu espíritu sobrevivirá.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:17:37.556 --> 00:17:39.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debo hacerlo.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento. No quiero, pero debo.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:17:42.728 --> 00:17:44.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué? Sabes que está mal.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:48.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un asesino no decide qué es correcto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>solo ve vida y muerte.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:17:48.817 --> 00:17:52.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ingenioso pero ¿lo crees?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo resuelve algo?</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:17:52.404 --> 00:17:55.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es justicia. Los humanos atacaron</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sin provocación.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:17:55.866 --> 00:17:57.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y está bien que hagan lo mismo?</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:17:58.035 --> 00:18:00.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pues no es lo mismo,</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:18:00.788 --> 00:18:03.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>porque atacamos provocados.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:18:03.916 --> 00:18:05.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entonces es un ciclo. Me lastimas</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:18:06.043 --> 00:18:09.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>y alguien se vengará de los elfos.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>No acabará.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:18:09.171 --> 00:18:10.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Callum.</i></c.bg_transparent>

199
00:18:11.298 --> 00:18:12.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Callum.</i></c.bg_transparent>

200
00:18:13.175 --> 00:18:14.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vete.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:18:14.802 --> 00:18:16.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Encontré algo.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:18:16.303 --> 00:18:18.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Hablas con la pintura?</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:18:18.806 --> 00:18:22.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué? ¿Por qué haría eso?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡No es buen momento!</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:18:23.519 --> 00:18:25.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Porque estás con una chica?</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:18:30.692 --> 00:18:31.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tarta de jalea?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:18:31.860 --> 00:18:34.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Niño, vete.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Callum, ¿qué pasa?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:18:34.488 --> 00:18:37.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Callum? Pensé que eras el príncipe Ezran.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:18:37.407 --> 00:18:38.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Me mentiste!</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:18:38.909 --> 00:18:40.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Es peor que matar?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:18:43.831 --> 00:18:46.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Conoces a Cebo?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Saluda a mi amiguito.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:18:53.173 --> 00:18:55.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Callum, sígueme.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Debo mostrarte algo.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:19:07.980 --> 00:19:11.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no me ocultaré en el cuerpo de otro</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:19:11.233 --> 00:19:14.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mientras alguien muere pagando</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por mis decisiones.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:19:14.695 --> 00:19:18.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doscientos hombres y mujeres están listos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para morir protegiéndote,</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:19:18.824 --> 00:19:22.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero ¿no dejarás</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que un soldado se sacrifique?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:19:22.119 --> 00:19:23.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es lo mismo.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:19:24.496 --> 00:19:28.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prefiero morir como rey que vivir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como cobarde.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:19:30.544 --> 00:19:33.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Así que de eso se trata.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿De qué hablas?</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:19:34.214 --> 00:19:35.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Orgullo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- No.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:19:35.966 --> 00:19:40.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya te dije el problema. Es magia oscura.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:19:40.387 --> 00:19:44.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí. Lo es. Es inteligente y brillante.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡Es práctico!</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:19:44.641 --> 00:19:47.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Salvará tu vida y la de muchos.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:19:47.311 --> 00:19:48.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un atajo.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:19:49.104 --> 00:19:52.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás no paguemos ahora,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero lo haremos al final.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:19:53.108 --> 00:19:56.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué crees que nos trajo aquí?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡Magia oscura!</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:19:57.070 --> 00:19:59.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estás siendo terco e ingrato.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:19:59.615 --> 00:20:02.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Debo agradecerte por destruir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>el huevo del dragón?</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:20:02.659 --> 00:20:05.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por comenzar esta guerra imposible</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de ganar?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:20:05.787 --> 00:20:08.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por enojar tanto a los dragones</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y elfos</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:20:08.916 --> 00:20:10.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>que hoy vienen por mi vida?</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:20:10.959 --> 00:20:14.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Destruir el huevo salvó a nuestro reino.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:20:14.379 --> 00:20:17.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Quizás a toda la humanidad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Era un huevo!</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:20:18.008 --> 00:20:21.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Y se hubiera convertido</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en lo más poderoso del mundo!</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:20:27.809 --> 00:20:30.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo hecho no puede ser deshecho.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:20:31.313 --> 00:20:34.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te ofrezco una alternativa.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:20:34.900 --> 00:20:37.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu incomodidad es comprensible.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:20:37.819 --> 00:20:41.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No sientes bien cambiar tu vida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por la de otro. Pero entiende.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:20:42.282 --> 00:20:46.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cada uno de estos hombres y mujeres</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>darían con gusto su vida</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:20:46.954 --> 00:20:48.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>para salvar la tuya.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:20:53.877 --> 00:20:55.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Y tú, Viren?</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:20:56.088 --> 00:20:57.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo...</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:21:00.175 --> 00:21:01.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vete.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:21:14.106 --> 00:21:16.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Hacen que sea peor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Peor? ¿Cómo?</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:21:16.984 --> 00:21:18.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Por aquí!</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:21:20.612 --> 00:21:22.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estamos atrapados.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué hacemos?</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:21:24.324 --> 00:21:25.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hora de un acertijo</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:21:26.994 --> 00:21:31.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Roca, roca, piedra, roca, piedra, piedra.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Roca, piedra, roca, piedra.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:21:32.040 --> 00:21:34.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cuál es la diferencia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>entre roca y piedra?</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:21:34.751 --> 00:21:37.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me hiciste usar piedra en vez de roca.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:21:37.254 --> 00:21:41.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Roca, roca, piedra, roca,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>piedra, piedra, roca, piedra, roca.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:21:53.562 --> 00:21:54.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vaya!</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:22:08.327 --> 00:22:11.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Sí!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Seguro que no nos seguirá?</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:22:11.121 --> 00:22:14.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>De ningún modo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Me tomó un mes descifrar eso.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:22:19.963 --> 00:22:21.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo la abriste?</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:22:21.631 --> 00:22:24.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Presioné las piedras</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con huellas de jalea.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:22:39.775 --> 00:22:41.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué es este lugar?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:22:42.527 --> 00:22:44.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Runaan tiene razón.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:22:44.446 --> 00:22:47.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No hay nada en los humanos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que valga la pena.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:22:47.991 --> 00:22:49.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se acabó el tiempo.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:22:49.826 --> 00:22:52.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los humanos destruyeron el huevo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del Príncipe Dragón.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:22:53.080 --> 00:22:54.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Debe haber justicia!</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:22:55.374 --> 00:22:57.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Tendrás que vencerme!</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:22:58.210 --> 00:22:59.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿De verdad?</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:22:59.878 --> 00:23:01.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera. Debes ver algo.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:23:02.214 --> 00:23:05.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No caeré por el truco</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de la rana brillante.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:23:05.300 --> 00:23:06.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un sapo luminoso.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:23:07.511 --> 00:23:10.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero no hay truco esta vez.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor, mira.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:23:13.725 --> 00:23:15.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bien. Descúbrelo.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:23:16.019 --> 00:23:17.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lentamente.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:23:17.854 --> 00:23:21.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oigo algo adentro que está vivo.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:23:27.280 --> 00:23:29.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puede ser.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:23:30.283 --> 00:23:32.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El huevo no fue destruido.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:24:17.414 --> 00:24:19.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
